Automated Smart Contract Auditing Tool

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Objective: Develop an advanced automated tool for auditing Solidity smart contracts.
Key Features:
Scan for a broad spectrum of security vulnerabilities and code inefficiencies.
User-friendly interface catering to various expertise levels.
Modular design for ease of updates and adding new features.
Compatibility across different Solidity versions and blockchain platforms.
Expanded Scope: Integrate predictive analytics for identifying potential future vulnerabilities.
Innovative Feature: Incorporate AI to learn from past audits and enhance future scans.
Creative Interpretation: Design an intuitive interface accessible to non-technical users.
Expected Deliverable: A cutting-edge auditing tool with comprehensive documentation, a user manual, 
and example audit reports showcasing its advanced features.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
